{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm going to make an argument today"},{"time":2000,"text":"that may seem a little bit crazy:"},{"time":5000,"text":"social media and the end of gender."},{"time":8000,"text":"Let me connect the dots."},{"time":11000,"text":"I'm going to argue today"},{"time":13000,"text":"that the social media applications"},{"time":15000,"text":"that we all know and love, or love to hate,"},{"time":18000,"text":"are actually going to help free us"},{"time":20000,"text":"from some of the absurd assumptions"},{"time":22000,"text":"that we have as a society about gender."},{"time":25000,"text":"I think that social media"},{"time":27000,"text":"is actually going to help us dismantle"},{"time":29000,"text":"some of the silly and demeaning stereotypes"},{"time":32000,"text":"that we see in media and advertising"},{"time":35000,"text":"about gender."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"If you hadn't noticed,"},{"time":39000,"text":"our media climate generally provides"},{"time":41000,"text":"a very distorted mirror"},{"time":43000,"text":"of our lives and of our gender,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and I think that's going to change."},{"time":47000,"text":"Now most media companies --"},{"time":49000,"text":"television, radio, publishing, games, you name it --"},{"time":52000,"text":"they use very rigid segmentation methods"},{"time":55000,"text":"in order to understand their audiences."},{"time":57000,"text":"It's old-school demographics."},{"time":59000,"text":"They come up with these very restrictive labels to define us."},{"time":64000,"text":"Now the crazy thing"},{"time":66000,"text":"is that media companies believe"},{"time":68000,"text":"that if you fall within a certain demographic category"},{"time":71000,"text":"then you are predictable in certain ways --"},{"time":73000,"text":"you have certain taste,"},{"time":75000,"text":"that you like certain things."},{"time":77000,"text":"And so the bizarre result of this"},{"time":79000,"text":"is that most of our popular culture"},{"time":81000,"text":"is actually based on these presumptions"},{"time":83000,"text":"about our demographics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":86000,"text":"Age demographics:"},{"time":88000,"text":"the 18 to 49 demo"},{"time":90000,"text":"has had a huge impact"},{"time":92000,"text":"on all mass media programming in this country"},{"time":94000,"text":"since the 1960s,"},{"time":96000,"text":"when the baby boomers were still young."},{"time":99000,"text":"Now they've aged out of that demographic,"},{"time":102000,"text":"but it's still the case"},{"time":104000,"text":"that powerful ratings companies like Nielson"},{"time":106000,"text":"don't even take into account"},{"time":108000,"text":"viewers of television shows over age 54."},{"time":111000,"text":"In our media environment,"},{"time":113000,"text":"it's as if they don't even exist."},{"time":115000,"text":"Now, if you watch \"Mad Men,\" like I do --"},{"time":117000,"text":"it's a popular TV show in the States --"},{"time":120000,"text":"Dr. Faye Miller does something called psychographics,"},{"time":123000,"text":"which first came about in the 1960s,"},{"time":126000,"text":"where you create these complex psychological profiles"},{"time":128000,"text":"of consumers."},{"time":130000,"text":"But psychographics really haven't had a huge impact on the media business."},{"time":133000,"text":"It's really just been basic demographics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":137000,"text":"So I'm at the Norman Lear Center at USC,"},{"time":140000,"text":"and we've done a lot of research over the last seven, eight years"},{"time":143000,"text":"on demographics"},{"time":145000,"text":"and how they affect media and entertainment"},{"time":147000,"text":"in this country and abroad."},{"time":149000,"text":"And in the last three years,"},{"time":151000,"text":"we've been looking specifically at social media to see what has changed,"},{"time":154000,"text":"and we've discovered some very interesting things."},{"time":158000,"text":"All the people who participate in social media networks"},{"time":160000,"text":"belong to the same old demographic categories"},{"time":163000,"text":"that media companies and advertisers"},{"time":165000,"text":"have used in order to understand them."},{"time":167000,"text":"But those categories mean even less now"},{"time":170000,"text":"than they did before,"},{"time":172000,"text":"because with online networking tools,"},{"time":174000,"text":"it's much easier for us"},{"time":176000,"text":"to escape some of our demographic boxes."},{"time":178000,"text":"We're able to connect with people quite freely"},{"time":181000,"text":"and to redefine ourselves online."},{"time":183000,"text":"And we can lie about our age online, too, pretty easily."},{"time":187000,"text":"We can also connect with people"},{"time":190000,"text":"based on our very specific interests."},{"time":192000,"text":"We don't need a media company"},{"time":194000,"text":"to help do this for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":196000,"text":"So the traditional media companies, of course,"},{"time":199000,"text":"are paying very close attention to these online communities."},{"time":202000,"text":"They know this is the mass audience of the future;"},{"time":205000,"text":"they need to figure it out."},{"time":207000,"text":"But they're having a hard time doing it"},{"time":209000,"text":"because they're still trying to use demographics in order to understand them,"},{"time":212000,"text":"because that's how ad rates are still determined."},{"time":215000,"text":"When they're monitoring your clickstream --"},{"time":217000,"text":"and you know they are --"},{"time":219000,"text":"they have a really hard time"},{"time":221000,"text":"figuring out your age, your gender and your income."},{"time":223000,"text":"They can make some educated guesses."},{"time":225000,"text":"But they get a lot more information"},{"time":227000,"text":"about what you do online,"},{"time":229000,"text":"what you like, what interests you."},{"time":231000,"text":"That's easier for them to find out than who you are."},{"time":234000,"text":"And even though that's still sort of creepy,"},{"time":237000,"text":"there is an upside"},{"time":239000,"text":"to having your taste monitored."},{"time":242000,"text":"Suddenly our taste is being respected"},{"time":244000,"text":"in a way that it hasn't been before."},{"time":246000,"text":"It had been presumed before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249000,"text":"So when you look online at the way people aggregate,"},{"time":252000,"text":"they don't aggregate"},{"time":254000,"text":"around age, gender and income."},{"time":256000,"text":"They aggregate around the things they love,"},{"time":258000,"text":"the things that they like,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and if you think about it, shared interests and values"},{"time":262000,"text":"are a far more powerful aggregator of human beings"},{"time":265000,"text":"than demographic categories."},{"time":267000,"text":"I'd much rather know"},{"time":269000,"text":"whether you like \"Buffy the Vampire Slayer\""},{"time":272000,"text":"rather than how old you are."},{"time":274000,"text":"That would tell me something more substantial about you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"Now there's something else that we've discovered about social media"},{"time":280000,"text":"that's actually quite surprising."},{"time":282000,"text":"It turns out that women"},{"time":284000,"text":"are really driving the social media revolution."},{"time":288000,"text":"If you look at the statistics --"},{"time":290000,"text":"these are worldwide statistics --"},{"time":292000,"text":"in every single age category,"},{"time":295000,"text":"women actually outnumber men"},{"time":297000,"text":"in their use of social networking technologies."},{"time":301000,"text":"And then if you look at the amount of time"},{"time":303000,"text":"that they spend on these sites,"},{"time":305000,"text":"they truly dominate the social media space,"},{"time":308000,"text":"which is a space that's having a huge impact"},{"time":311000,"text":"on old media."},{"time":313000,"text":"The question is: what sort of impact"},{"time":315000,"text":"is this going to have on our culture,"},{"time":318000,"text":"and what's it going to mean for women?"},{"time":320000,"text":"If the case is that social media"},{"time":322000,"text":"is dominating old media"},{"time":324000,"text":"and women are dominating social media,"},{"time":327000,"text":"then does that mean that women"},{"time":329000,"text":"are going to take over global media?"},{"time":331000,"text":"Are we suddenly going to see"},{"time":333000,"text":"a lot more female characters in cartoons"},{"time":335000,"text":"and in games and on TV shows?"},{"time":338000,"text":"Will the next big-budget blockbuster movies"},{"time":342000,"text":"actually be chick flicks?"},{"time":345000,"text":"Could this be possible,"},{"time":347000,"text":"that suddenly our media landscape"},{"time":349000,"text":"will become a feminist landscape?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":353000,"text":"Well, I actually don't think that's going to be the case."},{"time":356000,"text":"I think that media companies are going to hire a lot more women,"},{"time":359000,"text":"because they realize this is important for their business,"},{"time":361000,"text":"and I think that women"},{"time":363000,"text":"are also going to continue to dominate"},{"time":365000,"text":"the social media sphere."},{"time":367000,"text":"But I think women are actually going to be -- ironically enough --"},{"time":370000,"text":"responsible for driving a stake through the heart"},{"time":373000,"text":"of cheesy genre categories"},{"time":377000,"text":"like the \"chick flick\""},{"time":379000,"text":"and all these other genre categories"},{"time":381000,"text":"that presume that certain demographic groups"},{"time":384000,"text":"like certain things --"},{"time":386000,"text":"that Hispanics like certain things,"},{"time":388000,"text":"that young people like certain things."},{"time":390000,"text":"This is far too simplistic."},{"time":392000,"text":"The future entertainment media that we're going to see"},{"time":395000,"text":"is going to be very data-driven,"},{"time":397000,"text":"and it's going to be based on the information"},{"time":399000,"text":"that we ascertain from taste communities online,"},{"time":402000,"text":"where women are really driving the action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405000,"text":"So you may be asking, well why is it important"},{"time":408000,"text":"that I know what entertains people?"},{"time":410000,"text":"Why should I know this?"},{"time":412000,"text":"Of course, old media companies and advertisers"},{"time":414000,"text":"need to know this."},{"time":416000,"text":"But my argument is that,"},{"time":418000,"text":"if you want to understand the global village,"},{"time":420000,"text":"it's probably a good idea that you figure out"},{"time":422000,"text":"what they're passionate about, what amuses them,"},{"time":425000,"text":"what they choose to do in their free time."},{"time":428000,"text":"This is a very important thing to know about people."},{"time":431000,"text":"I've spent most of my professional life"},{"time":434000,"text":"researching media and entertainment"},{"time":436000,"text":"and its impact on people's lives."},{"time":438000,"text":"And I do it not just because it's fun --"},{"time":441000,"text":"though actually, it is really fun --"},{"time":443000,"text":"but also because"},{"time":445000,"text":"our research has shown over and over again"},{"time":447000,"text":"that entertainment and play"},{"time":449000,"text":"have a huge impact on people's lives --"},{"time":452000,"text":"for instance, on their political beliefs"},{"time":454000,"text":"and on their health."},{"time":456000,"text":"And so, if you have any interest in understanding the world,"},{"time":459000,"text":"looking at how people amuse themselves"},{"time":461000,"text":"is a really good way to start."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"So imagine a media atmosphere"},{"time":467000,"text":"that isn't dominated by lame stereotypes"},{"time":470000,"text":"about gender"},{"time":472000,"text":"and other demographic characteristics."},{"time":474000,"text":"Can you even imagine what that looks like?"},{"time":476000,"text":"I can't wait to find out what it looks like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":478000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":480000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}